name: Cathay Pacific Cargo 747-8F Takeoff from Paine Field ᴴᴰ
description:
25th Paine Field video!

Sorry for the bad quality, this was shot with a DSLR camera. Anyway, here we have a Cathay Pacific Boeing 747-8F departing Paine Field on a routine test flight. Glad I got to see this bird without any fog in the way!

Hmm... A Cathay Pacific plane... Oh, gee, who should I dedicate this to...

CATHAYA340!!! This one's for you, buddy :D
